Step 1. Create The Cluster

Login AWS Console -> Search Bar -> ECS -> Click On Elastic Container Service -> Clusters -> Create cluster -> Cluster name -> Create



Step 2. Create The Task Definition

Go To Task definitions Section -> Create new task definition -> Task definition family Name -> Container details -> Name -> Image URI(Image Name) -> Create



Step 3. Create The Service

Select The Cluster -> Services -> Create -> Select The Task definition family -> Networking -> Security group -> Security group name -> Create 



Step 4. Run The Service On Chrome

Select The Cluster -> Task -> Click The Task -> Scroll Down -> Public IP
